query:
SELECT p.id, p.serviceId, p.countryId, p.apiId, p.ourPrice, p.quantityAvailable, s.smshubCode, a.name as apiName
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa' AND p.countryId = 1
ORDER BY p.apiId
